        "timestamp": 1593422509
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I should mention a nice formalization in Isabelle: <a href=\"https://www.isa-afp.org/entries/Pi_Transcendental.html\">https://www.isa-afp.org/entries/Pi_Transcendental.html</a>. It should be possible to follow it essentially step by step in Lean!</p>",
