        "sender_full_name": "Johan Commelin",
        "timestamp": 1593423394
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I should say now that the student is <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"252627\">@Jujian Zhang</span> and he has warmed up by proving transcendence of e! He needed FTC and a couple of corollaries like integration by parts, but other than a few axioms the proof compiles!</p>",
        "id": 202594398,
